long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Revolutionize Your Chrome New Tab Experience with a Stunning Calendar and Instant Search Extension!

MyPlanner Extension offers a sleek Calendar view and shortcuts for new-level productivity.
By clicking “Add to Chrome”, you accept and agree to install the MyPlanner extension, set the Chrome™ new tab search to MyPlanner, and to the Terms of Use, and Privacy Policy.

The MyPlanner extension sets your new tab search provider to Microsoft Bing.

Terms of Use: https://myplanner.webplannerview.com/terms-of-use
Privacy Policy: https://myplanner.webplannerview.com/privacy-policy

Sleek Calendar View
Say goodbye to boring New Tab pages. Our extension brings a beautiful, intuitive calendar view to your Chrome browser, to quickly glance at your calendar, without leaving your browser.

Instant Search Box
Need to find something fast? Our extension integrates a powerful search box directly into your New Tab page. Effortlessly search the web, access bookmarks, or find your saved documents—all without opening a new tab or disrupting your workflow.
